{"id":9678,"date":"2020-06-26T13:11:46","date_gmt":"2020-06-26T11:11:46","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/?p=9678"},"modified":"2020-06-26T13:50:56","modified_gmt":"2020-06-26T11:50:56","slug":"glastonbury-blues-love-the-farm-miss-that-place","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/glastonbury-blues-love-the-farm-miss-that-place\/","title":{"rendered":"Glastonbury blues: Love the farm, miss that place"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>We\u2019re reminiscing about years gone by and the <strong>magic of Worthy Farm<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p><!--more--><\/p>\n<p>By now we\u2019d be well and truly settled in at a place we and so many others consider a home from home\u2026 Worthy Farm. Sadly, instead of a home from home, this year it&#8217;s #GlastoAtHome.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.glastonburyfestivals.co.uk\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Glastonbury<\/a> is a festival like no other, and everything from the familiar friendly faces to the spectacular setting makes it somewhere we hold so dear. With 2020 an impromptu fallow year, we\u2019re gutted not to be there to feed the wonderful crew who work so hard to build and manage this incredible event.<\/p>\n<p>Since 2013, there\u2019s been busy Radishes on that sacred land. Spending weeks on site and seeing it go from farm, to build, to break, to farm again; Glasto is the humble Radish\u2019s happy place every year. Rain or shine, mud bath or sun trap, there\u2019s nowhere like it.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-9680 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/mike-defender-1024x809.jpg\" alt=\"mike-defender-glasto\" width=\"1024\" height=\"809\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/mike-defender.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/mike-defender-300x237.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/mike-defender-768x607.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/mike-defender-480x379.jpg 480w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/mike-defender-840x664.jpg 840w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/mike-defender-600x474.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-9682 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/west-holts-trucks-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"west-holts-vans\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/west-holts-trucks.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/west-holts-trucks-225x300.jpg 225w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/west-holts-trucks-480x640.jpg 480w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/west-holts-trucks-600x800.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>This time of the summer brings out the best in the festival community, and with the sun beating down and iconic sets playing on the radio this weekend, it\u2019s hard not to feel nostalgic about years gone by.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Festival catering is at the heart of what we do at Red Radish<\/strong>, and Glastonbury epitomises it. We\u2019ll have everything crossed that 2021 can go ahead &#8211; what a party that\u2019ll be! Until then, Love and Peas.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-9681 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/glastobins-1024x682.jpg\" alt=\"glasto-bins\" width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/glastobins-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/glastobins-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/glastobins-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/glastobins-480x320.jpg 480w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/glastobins-840x560.jpg 840w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/glastobins-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/glastobins.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Glasto fans across the country are holding their own mini festivals, and we&#8217;ve been doing a bit of tinkering at our place too. It&#8217;s quite the transformation!<strong> Watch this space for our own little nod to Glastonbury<\/strong> \u2013 a bit of a celebration for our amazing team, who have been locked down together and working so hard over the past three months. #WeAreNotWorthy<\/p>\n<p><em>Find out more about our crew and artist catering on our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/festival-catering\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">festival catering<\/a> page. For TV and film work, you can read more in our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/tv-film-catering\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">location catering<\/a> section.<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>We\u2019re reminiscing about years gone by and the magic of Worthy Farm.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":13886,"featured_media":9679,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[27],"tags":[293,263,298,304,336,335,337],"class_list":["post-9678","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-festivals","tag-artist-catering","tag-crew-catering","tag-festival","tag-festival-catering","tag-glasto","tag-glastonbury","tag-worthy-farm"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v23.5 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\